comments:
Abolished 1.4.1974 to become an unparished area. See also Table 
    2, notes (a) and (f).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish  of Ashford. See 
    also Table 2, note (g).

Abolished 1.4.1987 and added to the Ashford unparished 
    area and the parishes Great Chart with Singleton, Hothfield and Kingsnorth. See 
    also Table 2, note (f).

Created 1.4.1987 out of the Ashford unparished area and part 
    of parish of Great Chart. See also Table 2, note (g).

Abolished 1.4.1987 and divided between the parishes of Mersham 
    and Wye with Hinxhill. See also Table 2, note (a).

Created 1.4.1987 out of the Ashford unparished area and part 
    of the parish of Kingsnorth. See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1.4.1987 from the parishes of Hinxhill and Wye. See 
    also Table 2, note (g).
